 {{{ - 7} \over {11}} + {4 \over {11}}} \right)}^2} + {{\left( {{7 \over {11}} - {4 \over {11}}} \right)}^2}} $$<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow O'P' = {1 \over {11}}\sqrt {4 + 9 + 9} $$<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow O'P' = {{\sqrt {22} } \over {11}}$$<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow O'P' = {{\sqrt 2  \times \sqrt {11} } \over {11}}$$<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow O'P' = \sqrt {{2 \over {11}}} $$

